name: xdCode Web Terminal
body:
### Welcome to xdCode Web Terminal
Sometimes we need to check something fast or to start daemon or just to kill process... and we cannot do it via putty or something like that... so you can access the xdCode Web Terminal via your laptop or even your smartphone. 


### Authors and Contributors
We are working as a team Nikolay Hristov (Developer), Adrean Boqjdiev (Developer) and George Nikolov (Front-end).

### Support or Contact
If you enjoy of the idea and want to help you can contact us on:
Strikebg@gmail.com
